DJabberd is an IM framework written in [[Perl]] where "everything is a plugin". The base code comes with some plugins, even:

* DJabberd-Authen-HTDigest
* DJabberd-Authen-MySQL
* DJabberd-Authen-PAM

I modified one:

* [[Djabberd/Docunext Modified DJabberd Authen LDAP]]

#### DJabberd on Debian

First I fixup CPAN

    install Bundle::CPAN
    force install Scalar::Util
    install Danga::Socket
    install Net::DNS
    install DBI
    install DBD::SQLite

then I install some debian packages...

    apt-get install libnet-ssleay-perl libxml2-dev libssl-dev openssl
